official_title: Deploring the ongoing violence by Iraqi security forces against the residents of Camp Ashraf in Iraq.

summary.text:
Deplores the violence by Iraqi security forces against the residents of Camp Ashraf.

Calls upon the Iraqi government and the President of the United States to ensure the security and protection of Camp Ashraf residents.
